<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>MiniCrm - Welcome to CRM</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'welcome', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>

  <body>

<% if flash[:message] %>
      <div class="notice"><%= flash[:message] %></div>
<% end %>

  <header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-3 mb-4 border-bottom">
        <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto text-dark text-decoration-none">
            <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32"><use xlink:href="#bootstrap"></use></svg>
            <span class="fs-4">Mini CRM</span>
        </a>

        <ul class="nav nav-pills">
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page">Home</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/welcome-to-crm" class="nav-link">Get Started</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/login" class="nav-link">Sign In</a></li>
        </ul>
    </header>

    <main>
  
    <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Project Details</h1>
      <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
        <p class="lead mb-4">
        <ul>
        <li><b>Contact Management:</b></li>
        <ul>
          <li>Both user can be easily managed contacts. User can add and create contact with contact name, email and other information.</li>
        </ul>
        <li><b>Identity Management:</b></li>
        <ul>
          <li>In identity management, anonomous visitor are are tracked are able to be linked to contact record if the lead gives their email. Users might use different browsers, move from a mobile device to a laptop, or periodically clear browsing data.
           Identity management system offers the ability to link anonomous movements across different platforms, giving a holistic view of the user journey.</li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
        
        </p>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
        <%= yield %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </main>
    
    </body>
</html>
